Need openMw 0.49


By searching in existing plants for seeds and with a Miner's pick, you can plant new seeds for farming.
Plants have 5% chance to have seed (this up with time).


Hit the ground with a Miner's pick to create a clod.
Equip a seed and activate the clod to plant the seed an a young plant pop-up.

Take care of your youngs plants (by activating) and they will grow faster.


Each day, the plant have a chance to grow :
- 5% chance to grow
- +30% if you take care of it
- +5% for each plant in the same cell (water or ground) 

After 10 grow, the plant is fully grown and (should) give ingredients/seeds.
